Package: mnemos-cix-integration
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Jason Perlow <jason.perlow@gmail.com>
Depends: python3-venv, python3-pip, cix-noe-umd
Description: MNEMOS CIX NPU Embedding integration
 Contains the pre-compiled MiniLM-L6-v2 ONNX graph for the Zhouyi V3 NPU,
 alongside a FastAPI wrapper to expose it natively to MNEMOS via an OpenAI
 compatible /v1/embeddings endpoint.
